messages.message: Great demo by @Chris and @Venkatesh from Cass on our RFP chatbot. A key requirement for them to use this at scale is to call the chatbot via API, provide a list of questions to ask the RFP that correspond to the customer-specific RFP request, and then the ability to integrate the responses in an internal system or export as an excel spreadsheet (cc: @avi@Varun Jain). Exciting to see our enterprise customers explore use cases outside of IDP!
